WEBVTT

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:28.920
Hey.

00:00:45.120 --> 00:00:47.160
Bathing in orchid water

00:00:47.640 --> 00:00:50.960
Wearing colorful clothes like flowers.

00:01:28.080 --> 00:01:28.560
This...

00:01:28.640 --> 00:01:29.100
This...

00:01:35.759 --> 00:01:37.020
How could this happen?

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:42.280
What a pity.

00:01:45.280 --> 00:01:47.080
I've sinned. Please forgive me, sir.

00:01:47.080 --> 00:01:48.680
What sin have you committed?

00:01:48.880 --> 00:01:51.440
I know my body is hideous.

00:01:51.880 --> 00:01:53.740
Yet I dared to be in your painting.

00:01:54.320 --> 00:01:55.979
I've truly offended your eyes

00:01:56.080 --> 00:01:57.600
and insulted your intentions.

00:01:57.600 --> 00:01:58.660
This is a great sin.

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:01.290
I, Nongyu, willingly accept punishment.

00:02:02.240 --> 00:02:03.700
You've been through a lot.

00:02:05.080 --> 00:02:06.320
But your body

00:02:06.640 --> 00:02:08.840
truly isn't worthy of my paintings.

00:02:10.680 --> 00:02:11.480
However...

00:02:12.040 --> 00:02:14.920
It's a pity about your pretty face.

00:02:15.880 --> 00:02:18.540
Just focus on brewing your medicine from now on.

00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:25.480
Shiyuan.

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:27.640
Let's go for a walk.

00:02:27.920 --> 00:02:28.720
Yes, sir.

00:02:38.240 --> 00:02:38.960
Li Ling.

00:02:39.079 --> 00:02:40.740
Since we've known each other,

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:44.050
this is the first time I've seen you like this.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:45.760
I truly miss

00:02:45.760 --> 00:02:47.620
the days when we fought together,

00:02:47.960 --> 00:02:49.800
wielding guns and riding horses,

00:02:49.800 --> 00:02:51.329
living life to the fullest.

00:02:53.480 --> 00:02:55.000
Not like now,

00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:57.520
stuck in this den of snakes and rats,

00:02:58.400 --> 00:02:59.760
living like insects,

00:03:00.480 --> 00:03:02.400
existing like walking corpses.

00:03:04.440 --> 00:03:06.440
Who cares about these evil spirits?

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:09.000
Better to cut them down with one stroke.

00:03:10.240 --> 00:03:12.100
It's because of Nongyu, isn't it?

00:03:13.640 --> 00:03:16.440
The Night Firefly Painting isn't in our hands yet.

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:19.040
We can't afford any complications now.

00:03:19.240 --> 00:03:20.560
I'm sure I don't need to tell you

00:03:20.560 --> 00:03:22.440
that you understand what's at stake.

00:03:22.440 --> 00:03:23.480
As for that woman,

00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:25.329
her mind is extraordinary.

00:03:25.560 --> 00:03:26.800
Not just Chen Jingbian,

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:27.760
but you and I

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:29.760
are already under her control.

00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:30.360
She said

00:03:32.320 --> 00:03:33.650
she only wants revenge.

00:03:33.760 --> 00:03:35.620
If she truly only wanted revenge,

00:03:36.040 --> 00:03:38.440
do you think Wei Cheng would still be alive?

00:03:38.600 --> 00:03:40.260
Whether Wei Cheng is her enemy

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:41.440
is uncertain now.

00:03:41.800 --> 00:03:42.840
A woman who's willing

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:44.160
to risk her own life

00:03:44.760 --> 00:03:46.440
If there comes a day,

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:48.860
she will show you no mercy either.

00:03:49.600 --> 00:03:51.120
When she tried to kill herself,

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:52.920
you shouldn't have stopped her.

00:03:53.280 --> 00:03:54.340
But no matter what,

00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:56.930
I couldn't just stand by and watch.

00:03:58.040 --> 00:03:58.770
After all...

00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:02.880
After all, she saved A'qi's life.

00:04:03.720 --> 00:04:04.780
Li Ling, oh Li Ling.

00:04:06.200 --> 00:04:07.530
